r>I can bow kite just about anything that can be snared/rooted; however it takes me a good 15-20 minutes per kill.  Its very long and VERY boring and I dont do it often for that reason.<br><br>Dont worry Elexion......you dont seem to be too far off from where I am.  I dont even have any haste items.<br><br>I dunno.....At L53 I had hoped for a LOT more than this.  I took the ranger BECAUSE of the bow and so far...I've been sadly disappointed.<br> <p>SanzaStarkRanger of Tunare 52nd season"Oh no!....the raynjur died AGAIN..."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#006400><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/upjkeajungleheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pjkea Jungleheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#ADFF2f>(1/14/02 4:15:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=155.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: trueshot</span><hr size=1> the trueshot disc can be used starting at lvl 51 so sorry to say sanza but you have been able to use this disc for quite some time <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#006400><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/ujackwood.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jackwood</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ADFF2f>(1/15/02 5:52:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=155.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: trueshot</span><hr size=1> Trueshot disc is at Lv55 not 51 , but u do get the chance to do double damage at 51+ but this is not the /disc<br>You get the resestance /disc at 51 , fearless at 54 , Trueshot at 55 and I think weapon shield is at 59 <br>I too would like to know how some high end rangers can do 800 crits and 100 avg damage <br><br>Jackwood Hawkeyes<br>52nd Ranger of Twisted Dreams <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#006400><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/uphylok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Phylok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#ADFF2f>(1/16/02 4:25:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=155.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Archery</span><hr size=1> I have had some interesting luck with Archery.  By pure luck of the dice. I scored 3 consecutive crits.  I don't think I will ever see something like that again.  But the damage was nice when kiting a mammoth calf. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#006400><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/ukaifus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kaifus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ADFF2f>(1/16/02 8:08:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=155.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Archery</span><hr size=1> Rangers are some evil mofos now with the alt xp and archery  buffs....<br><br>right now with a velium recurve bow ( 30 39 )  , 255 dex, 240 archery and falcon eye, my max trueshot is over 800<br><br>I plan on going even higher when i get the alt xp for archery mastery.  You know the one that increases bow shots by 100 percent...hehe<br><br>Imagine cracking something for 1600pts at a 200 range...hehe..manaless wizzie anyone...<br><br>Taadien Stormrunner<br>60th level warder of the glade<br>black tower - xegony <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr